name: 2012-noaa-ortho-rectified-near-infrared-mllw-mosaic-of-alabama-bon-secour-bay-and-weeks-bay-ner
notes: This data set contains ortho-rectified mosaic tiles, created as a product from the NOAA Integrated Ocean and Coastal Mapping (IOCM) initiative. The source imagery was acquired from 20121113 - 20121114. The images were acquired with an Applanix Digital Sensor System (DSS). The original images were acquired at a higher resolution than the final ortho-rectified mosaic.
